<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="button-v">button <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bʌtn/    美 /'bʌtn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 扣上扣子；（把……）扣紧：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>button one’s coat
把外衣纽扣扣紧</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Men’s clothes tend to button from the right, and women’s from the left.
男装通常是从右边扣的，而女装则是从左边。</p><footer>2010 重庆</footer></div></div>